title: Top 10 Tight End Rankings: George Kittle or Travis Kelce the best in the game? (Football 7/3)
description:
To rank the Top 10 tight ends in the NFL, Will Brinson welcomes Cody Benjamin to discuss his recent list on CBSSports.com. Austin Hooper switched teams this offseason, but will he have the same success in Cleveland with Baker Mayfield as he did in Atlanta with Matt Ryan? Rob Gronkowski is back in the league and back with Tom Brady, but can he remain one of the game's elites? Is the position dominated by a 'Big 3' or a 'Big 2'. Basically, does Zach Ertz belong in the conversation with George Kittle and Travis Kelce? All that and more on this episode of the Pick Six podcast.
'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox, Bullhorn and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
